title: NZV8 Magazine. Issue 67. December 2010.
description:
NZV8 Magazine. Issue 67. December 2010.

English | 104 pages | PDF | 70.82 Mb

NZV8 Magazine was conceived when the passionate muscle car scene was in 
need of an authority. Thanks to a large population of baby boomers, muscle 
car and V8 culture is starting to boom again in New Zealand. NZV8 is not 
only riding that wave, but leading the way by providing world class magazine 
that features the cars, events and people that make the scene so exciting. 
NZV8 covers an extensive range of high-performance V8-engine vehicles. 
Wherever the local ground shakes to the beat of a tuned eight-cylinder 
machine, NZV8 is part of the action.

Enjoy.
